{"tid":188832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好笑我切","createTime":"2017-04-06T03:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T04:11:19.000Z","uid":67026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a54aa7ad41e9c245b5fd84de03d0ab24ac6d8b6","tid":188832,"uid":67026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"有三個朋友結伴到一個與世隔絕既島探險，佢地行左入樹林入面，無意間發現到一個女人係度沖涼，然後就俾一班族人捉住左，原來個女人係當地族長的老婆。<br />\n<br />\n族長好嬲，決定要狠狠地懲罰佢地三個。<br />\n「我俾兩條路你地揀，一，除褲俾我地在座既每位族人彈賓州一下，彈完就放你地。二，死刑！」<br />\n<br />\n朋友A好爽快揀左懲罰一，俾百幾個族人各彈完一下之後訓左係地典下典下。<br />\n<br />\n朋友B好怕，但覺得「留得青山在，哪怕無柴燒」，所以都不情願地揀左懲罰一，點知有多百幾個族人打完獵返黎，即係一共俾二百幾個人彈賓州，完成之後嘔哂白泡。<br />\n<br />\n朋友C係一條漢子，士可殺不可辱，賓州係男人雄風既象徵，唔可以俾人玩弄。「我寧願死！」<br />\n族長聽到之後就回答：「好，人黎！彈佢賓州彈到佢死為止！」"},{"pid":"7f91f0db981ec452db279cc40b96de252311008a","tid":188832,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑左"},{"pid":"9ce8c76e9607b1993716cf95b960503f0a937fbe","tid":188832,"uid":25099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"onon99"},{"pid":"7d935e240a10588144175b7e9ddbdbe805a5def5","tid":188832,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:52:50.000Z","msg":"imom"},{"pid":"c7bb520223f014df6a826793bfa76f481426cb7b","tid":188832,"uid":49593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23caf285cc0e9a1148e29cfdc592713a8f02aeca","tid":188832,"uid":29126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8f0ac0a19a1fe9ee543730ba0bb43f33153bdbd","tid":188832,"uid":31002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:57:34.000Z","msg":"點解連登無結冰icon"},{"pid":"57ba15f8003b8404d51278c16f569cd57bdf6ffc","tid":188832,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}